title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table with highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
Steps to Reproduce:
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row.
SR:
1. Open the report attached.
2. Navigate to the table that has a group row containing a highlight rule and a map rule.
3. Preview the report.
4. Attempt to export the data from the table.
